<div class="wrapper wrapper_padding clearfix">
	<div class="col-1 about homepage_content">
		<h2>About</h2>
		<hr>
		<p>I am currently travelling in South East Asia for 3 and a half months. </p>
		<p><b>Current Location:</b> Ao Nang - Thailand</p>
		<p><b>Next Location:</b> Ko Phangan - Thailand</p>
